# Flutter Hybrid Development Playbook

When implementing Flutter work:

- Keep package boundaries, reuse, and bridge ownership clear.
- Split large widgets and feature logic cleanly.
- Comment shared packages, bridge contracts, and business-critical state.
- If UI design is involved, also follow the repository's admin UI quality rules.
